OL,3,CDesigner Paul Smith lends stylish hand
OL,4,Cto decorate tree at the Royal Opera
OL,5,CHouse
OL,7,FRenowned British fashion designer,
OL,8,FPaul Smith, whose tailoring became a
OL,9,Fhallmark of modern British style has
OL,10,Fbeen recruited by Covent Garden's
OL,11,FRoyal Opera House to give their
OL,12,FChristmas tree a stylish makeover.
OL,14,FPaul Smith, 79, opened his his first
OL,15,FLondon shop nearby in 1979 which
OL,16,Fbecame his design base and flagship
OL,17,Fstore.
