OL,3,CDesigner Paul Smith lends stylish hand
OL,4,Cto decorate tree at the Royal Opera
OL,5,CHouse
OL,7,FThe shop famously sold his bold
OL,8,Fpatterns, bright linings, and unique
OL,9,Fcolour combinations and today the area
OL,10,Fstill holds special meaning for him.
OL,12,F"When I came here the place was
OL,13,Fcompletely empty apart from the
OL,14,FUnderground station, two pubs and the
OL,15,FRoyal Opera House," Smith told ITV
OL,16,FNews London.
OL,18,F"So it just seems like the perfect fix
OL,19,Freally doing a tree.
