OL,3,CDesigner Paul Smith lends stylish hand
OL,4,Cto decorate tree at the Royal Opera
OL,5,CHouse
OL,7,F"The marvellous thing about doing the
OL,8,Ftree was I was allowed in the props
OL,9,Fdepartment at the back, so that was
OL,10,Fbrilliant.
OL,12,F"I could hunt through all the boxes...
OL,13,Fand all the props here.
OL,15,F"So we took a lot of the props for the
OL,16,Ftree that related to an opera," Smith
OL,17,Fexplained.
