OL,7,FAsked how he wanted people to feel
OL,8,Fwhen they saw his Christmas Tree,
OL,9,FSmith replied: "It's open to the
OL,10,Fpublic, so it's upstairs in the Paul
OL,11,FHamlin Room.
OL,13,F"Don't just stand and look at it
OL,14,Fbecause there's so much detail and
OL,15,Fthere's so much the emotion linked to
OL,16,Fit.
OL,18,F"So take time to look at."
