OL,4,Cto decorate tree at the Royal Opera
OL,5,CHouse
OL,7,FPaul Smith's global brand now includes
OL,8,Fover 130 shops in more than 65
OL,9,Fcountries and he remains involved with
OL,10,Fhis London studio.
OL,12,FAnd while business is thriving, the
OL,13,Fdesigner acknowledged the challenges
OL,14,Ffacing so many brands and
OL,15,Fentrepreneurs - including
OL,16,Finternational visitors no longer able
OL,17,Fto claim VAT refunds on goods
OL,18,Fpurchased in London.
