OL,7,FPaul Smith added: "I've been sort of
OL,8,Ffighting my corner for that for a few
OL,9,Fyears because it definitely has a huge
OL,10,Feffect.
OL,12,F"We had Brexit, which was a nightmare.
OL,13,FWe've had Covid, which was a triple
OL,14,Fnightmare."
